{"tid":102474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(進化)中國人活在污染中 學者﹕身體已適應","createTime":"2017-01-31T15:58:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T04:28:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8df668247d514013ee4bd601b94e5ef7035b302a","tid":102474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20170131/s00046/1485854453923SF_AD54E3BEA57A797A22BBF314357917A9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20170131%2Fs00046%2F1485854453923SF_AD54E3BEA57A797A22BBF314357917A9.jpg&h=e1f1bda3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】為了準確推算空氣污染引致提早死亡率，中文大學地理與資源管理學系助理教授嚴鴻霖表示，曾蒐集大量內地空氣污染、發病及死亡率等數據，發現中國人對空氣污染的反應沒外國明顯，估計與中國人長期處於較差的空氣質素有關。<br />\n<strong>其他報道：每年1700港人 遭內地毒霧催命</strong><br />\n嚴鴻霖表示，外國有不少研究顯示，污染物濃度與呼吸道疾病的發病率、入院率及提早死亡率有一定關係，若以世界衛生組織的方程式推算，中國每年因空氣污染而導致提早死亡的人數達147.2萬人；若採用美國環保署的標準，死亡人數更高達268.9萬人；經他重新調整的方程式，死亡人數下降至約87萬人。<br />\n他說，人民長期在空氣污染濃度較高的環境生活，令身體較為適應惡劣環境，故對空氣污染的反應相對外國較輕微，空氣污染而提早死亡的個案反而較少。<br />\n若採美國標準 死亡達270萬<br />\n世衛報告顯示，2014年全球有700萬人因空氣污染提早死亡；由港大學者開發的「達理指數」顯示，本港每年約有3200人因空氣污染而提早死亡，如以中大最新研究結果推算，即每年本港提早死亡個案之中，約一半是內地空氣污染導致。<br />\n事實上，環境局於2015年回覆立法會議員質詢時表示，港府研究微細懸浮粒子（PM2.5）來源，發現本港PM2.5當中有70%來自中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170131/s00002/1485798614218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170131%2Fs00002%2F1485798614218&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7LwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=cf0a854a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170131%2Fs00002%2F1485798614218&h=418005b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170131/s00002/1485798614218</a>"},{"pid":"0836dcb34d78d042030c540dd8ccecb23a854423","tid":102474,"uid":46255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"新人類"},{"pid":"0052b01f3504445e60e1d3279c273dbdc29e1a33","tid":102474,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:13:51.000Z","msg":"人類界既小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾時識飛？"},{"pid":"bdc154a754943d093b97121d1ff792cb7e3dd37e","tid":102474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07ec162842fd183c9d6a831028649971dbf0a09","tid":102474,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef5cad8e5f5ad7742b20e993d59f64874f220e8","tid":102474,"uid":50776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:51:47.000Z","msg":"進化論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650f6049bb3e30931e1246346d1468132e70861b","tid":102474,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:58:23.000Z","msg":"聰明使徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d23c2bd4b4f09fc6c84a41510e0c5eec94609c","tid":102474,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:58:45.000Z","msg":"遲啲玩埋核幅射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729406f9e6499f25f25de2f9d119e2c6a2345afb","tid":102474,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:02:31.000Z","msg":"仲以為係大陸磚家，點知係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /